that I would make alliances

01:20:08.448 --> 01:20:09.747
with older boys,

01:20:09.748 --> 01:20:11.350
you know, like, just one or two

01:20:11.351 --> 01:20:13.189
who would be my protectors.

01:20:16.189 --> 01:20:18.991
The summer when I was about ten,

01:20:18.992 --> 01:20:21.193
one of the older boys
who I depended on

01:20:21.194 --> 01:20:25.665
to kind of be a protector, his
name was Michael Schwerner.

01:20:25.666 --> 01:20:30.435
In the summer of '64,
I learned that Mickey

01:20:30.436 --> 01:20:37.376
had been in Mississippi
registering voters.

01:20:37.377 --> 01:20:41.913
And he and two other people
who had been with him

01:20:41.914 --> 01:20:45.718
registering voters were...

01:20:45.719 --> 01:20:48.056
were tortured and murdered.

01:20:51.056 --> 01:20:54.193
And when I heard
that my protector

01:20:54.194 --> 01:21:01.002
had been murdered
by the real bullies...

01:21:03.002 --> 01:21:06.138
I think it changed my life.

01:21:06.139 --> 01:21:10.108
I had to protect people
from the bullies,

01:21:10.109 --> 01:21:12.344
the people who would
beat them up economically

01:21:12.345 --> 01:21:15.480
or the people who would subject
them and their families

01:21:15.481 --> 01:21:18.082
to real harm.

01:21:18.083 --> 01:21:19.751
Because if you don't
have a voice,

01:21:19.752 --> 01:21:21.120
if you don't have power,

01:21:21.121 --> 01:21:23.956
if you are vulnerable
economically in society,

01:21:23.957 --> 01:21:27.033
you don't have anybody
to protect you.

01:21:34.033 --> 01:21:37.536
There's no single magic bullet

01:21:37.537 --> 01:21:38.871
to solving this problem.

01:21:38.872 --> 01:21:40.540
I mean, I've written
a lot of books.

01:21:40.541 --> 01:21:43.442
I've come up with a lot
of policy ideas.

01:21:43.443 --> 01:21:47.248
I'm not alone.
Policy ideas are plentiful.

01:21:49.248 --> 01:21:52.684
Remember, we make the rules
of the economy.

01:21:52.685 --> 01:21:56.658
And we have the power
to change those rules.

01:21:57.658 --> 01:22:00.960
You've got to mobilize.
You've got to organize.

01:22:00.961 --> 01:22:04.196
You've got to energize
other people.

01:22:04.197 --> 01:22:08.033
Politics is not out there.

01:22:08.034 --> 01:22:10.873
It starts here.

01:22:13.873 --> 01:22:16.774
Today's our last...
our last class.

